                </div>
                
                <div style="display:inline">
                    <div class="image" style="display:inline; margin-right: 0"><img src="/images/petition.jpg" style="width:300px; height:200px; margin-right: 20px;"></div>
                    <u><p style="display:inline">***The Office of the Governor is the sponsor of this petition, but is NOT the group requesting donations of any kind. You are able to sign the petition without donating to ipetitions which is the platform hosting the petition. No donations to ipetitions is required. DO NOT DONATE.***</p>
                    </u></br><br>
